Definition: in a blunt direct manner
Example: he spoke bluntly; he stated his opinion flat-out; he was criticized roundly
Synonyms: adj, all, direct, bluff, bluntly, blunt, brusquely, discourteous, brusque, flat_out, roundly, in, a, manner, he, spoke, stated, his, opinion, flat-out, was, criticized
Category: adv.all
